{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_09_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 踊ることは呼吸と一緒",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、僕と君はどうして\n仕事をキャンセルしてまで、こんな所にいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ why are you and I\nin a place like this‚ even canceling work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵の夏休みの宿題と特別課題をやるためだ\nほら、よそ見しない。集中して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To do your summer vacation homework and special assignments‚ Aoi.\nCome on‚ don't look around. Concentrate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 13.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕、高校辞めるって言ったよね？\nだったら、やらなくても良くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said I was going to quit high school‚ didn't I?\nThen I don't need to do this‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "高校は辞めないでくれ\n莉央さんにだって同じように言われただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't quit high school.\nRio-san told you the same thing‚ didn't she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "どうして辞めちゃいけないの？\n僕はダンスと歌で生きていくって決めたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why can't I quit?\nI decided to live through dance and song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3000747475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "葵の才能と実力は俺も認める\nでも、芸能の道で成功するにはいろんな経験が必要だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I acknowledge your talent and ability too‚ Aoi.\nBut you need various experiences to succeed in entertainment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんにも忠告されただろ？\n学生としての体験も大事だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san warned you too‚ didn't she?\nThat student experiences are also important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕は学生であることにこだわりはないんだけど\n……それでも、学校に行かないとダメ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not particular about being a student…\n…even so‚ do I have to go to school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今、この瞬間にしか体験出来ないことがあるんだよ\n学校だけが全てじゃないが、経験の一つにはなるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are things you can only experience at this very moment.\nSchool isn't everything‚ but it should be one experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 57
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕には分からないな\n……でも、君と莉央がそう言うなら、そうなのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't understand.\n…But if you and Rio say so‚ maybe that's right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今は納得出来ないかもしれないけど、信じてくれ\n……さぁ、宿題やって。分からないところは聞いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might not be convinced now‚ but please trust me.\n…Come on‚ do your homework. Ask me if there's anything you don't understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……。宿題だけじゃなくて、課題まであるから\n凄く大変だな。夏休み中に終わるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… Not just homework‚ but even assignments‚\nso it's really tough. Will it finish during summer vacation?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "悪いけど、宿題と課題が終わるまで\n仕事やレッスンのスケジュールは制限させてもらう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ but until the homework and assignments are finished‚\nI'll have to limit your work and lesson schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……君、意外と鬼だね\n仕方ない。手分けしてやろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're surprisingly ruthless.\nCan't be helped. Let's divide the work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、手分けすれば二倍の速さで――\nって、葵が全部やるんだよ。俺は見張ってるだけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ if we divide it‚ it'll be twice as fast――\nWait‚ you're doing it all‚ Aoi. I'm just watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "つれないな、君は\n一つくらい手伝ってくれてもいいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're cold.\nYou could help with at least one thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "自分でやらないと身につかないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't do it yourself‚ you won't learn‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 112.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "なら日誌だけでいいからさ\nそれなら、学力とは関係ないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then just the diary would be fine.\nThat's not related to academic ability‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いや、でも俺、葵の身に起きたこと\n全部は知らないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ but I don't know everything\nthat happened to you‚ Aoi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもいいよ。最近あったことは……着替えの時\n莉央や愛とサイズを比べて落ち込んだことかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anything's fine. Something that happened recently… when changing clothes‚\nI got depressed after comparing sizes with Rio and Ai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "サイズって……\n……そんなの俺が書けないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sizes…\n…I can't write about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 143.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央はともかく、年下の愛にまで負けた時の敗北感は\n――うん、かなりのものだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting Rio aside‚ the sense of defeat when I lost even to younger Ai\n――yeah‚ it was quite something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "何年も毎日牛乳を飲んでるのに\nどうして大きくならないんだろう。君はどう思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I've been drinking milk every day for years‚\nwhy don't I grow bigger? What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 152.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "頼むからそんなこと、俺に聞かないでくれ……\nとにかく、日誌も自分で書くこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't ask me about that…\nAnyway‚ write the diary yourself too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ、僕、いつ仕事に復帰出来るのかな？\nこの調子じゃ、来年までかからない？",
      "translations": {
